description: Outline planning application for a comprehensive, phased, mixed use development of land at harrow view and headstone drive, as set out in the development specification (march 2012). The development comprises the demolition of existing buildings and structures and redevelopment of the site for a mix of uses comprising business and employment uses, student accomodation, senior living, assisted care and retail and restaurant uses.
